N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 340.6 - Decision of committee

State Regulations

The Podiatry Practice Committee shall consist of three
members, two of whom shall constitute a quorum and may proceed with the
transaction of such business as may come before them, and a decision by a
majority of the committee shall be deemed the decision of the entire
committee. Notes
